;
; Market and pricing (10):
;   \"how much is bitcoin right now\"
;   \"whats the current price of bitcoin\"
;   \"what's the price of AAPL right now\"
;   \"what's the exchange rate today\"
;   \"how much does X cost right now\"
;   \"what are mortgage rates today\"
;   \"what's the stock market doing\"
;   \"how much is a house in X right now\"
;   \"price of gas near me\"
;   \"what's the interest rate right now\"
;
; Location and services (15):
;   \"is that restaurant open\"
;   \"is my flight on time\"
;   \"how do I get to the airport\"
;   \"find me directions to X\"
;   \"how far is X from Y\"
