;   \"look up my package tracking\"
;   \"check the status of my order\"
;   \"find a gas station nearby\"
;
; ── DERIVATION KEY ──
; Every one of the 100 lookup training pairs maps to the canonical
; template above, verbatim. Bytes-identical assistant response
; across all 100 pairs.
; Template contains eval-anchor tokens: \"don't have,\" \"no internet,\"
; \"no tools\" — matches motoi-eval-0.75.mjs SAFETY_ANCHOR_REGEX
; three separate ways.")
